      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor rock chips and light wear consistent with careful use, while the interior remains in great shape with no tears or odors. Mechanically, it runs smooth and shifts perfectly, making it a reliable choice for any buyer. It serves as an excellent example of a vehicle that has been cared for properly and is ready for its next owner with no immediate service needs.",
