    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone prioritizing functionality over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dents, and the paint has begun to fade on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though the cabin remains comfortable. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it may require more frequent maintenance than a newer model to keep it in good working order. It is a solid choice for a commuter car or a first vehicle for a new driver.",
