      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for checking out my car. It's been a fantastic, reliable ride for me, and I've really taken care of it over the years. It's in solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip! It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is looking for a new home. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
