    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 987.2 Cayman S powered by the 3.4L naturally aspirated DFI flat-six. This mid-engine platform excels in torsional rigidity and balanced polar moment of inertia. The 6-speed manual transmission offers short, tactile throws with a recently inspected clutch assembly showing strong bite. Features include a sport-tuned suspension with refreshed bushings and a communicative hydraulic steering rack. The engine pulls linearly to the redline with no evidence of bore scoring or IMS issues common in earlier generations. Minor road rash is present on the front fascia, but the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system integrity and brake rotor thickness\u2014are within optimal operating parameters.",
      "price": 36800.0,
